				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Monks are the supreme of warriors!  I, myself, am an agnostic, but I do respect those who follow Quellious and his tranquil thoughts.  I am a traveler of sorts, and though I am not as skilled as a disciple (or grandmaster), I find that you are fine with what you have at any level.  Your skills should be spread, you don't have to dump massive points into any one skill.  Trust me, I spread out my skills, now I hit faster, harder, and dodge strikes more often.  Trust me.<BR>
<BR>
Ezurate &lt;Mystic Rings of Norrath&gt;<BR>
Monk of the 6th fist
