			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Mycroft's original post nicely sums up the first 20 or so lvls; the only thing that I would add would be that SNEAK can actually be very useful, especially if you solo.  Without access to a gate spell monks are screwed if they are attacked by higher lvl NPC's with no guards around; sneak at a high lvl will make most NPC's indifferent to you.  As long as you con as much as possible, this skill makes it safe to roam zones with little fear of unwanted NPC's (without circling around).<BR>
<BR>
It is also helpful in bad areas where you need to retrieve your or anothers corpse.  <BR>
<BR>
Reuel lvl 19<BR>
Silent Fist<BR>

