				Now at lvl 25 i find myself wishing sometimes i had gotten 1hb up with my h2h.  Now that im almost high enough to get some decent 1hb like Fighting baton and Sap of Piety.  So keep up both.  And if you can get a light 2hb GET ONE!<BR>
