Humans Feign death is well... sad.<BR>
Iksar's Fiegn is cool.<BR>
Hard to decide which Flying kick is cooler.<BR>
I kinda like the Human instill doubt better.<BR>
Iksars get regen.<BR>
Humans aernt KoS everywhere.<BR>
<BR>
